%% ML Metadata (MLMD) - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant KFP as Kubeflow Pipelines<br/>(DSP Backend)
    participant MLMD as MLMD gRPC Server<br/>8080/TCP gRPC/HTTP2
    participant DB as MySQL/PostgreSQL<br/>3306/TCP or 5432/TCP

    Note over KFP,DB: Flow 1: Pipeline Run Metadata Recording

    KFP->>MLMD: PutExecution (pipeline run)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2, Optional TLS/mTLS
    MLMD->>DB: INSERT execution record<br/>MySQL/PostgreSQL protocol, Optional SSL
    DB-->>MLMD: Execution ID
    MLMD-->>KFP: PutExecutionResponse

    KFP->>MLMD: PutArtifacts (datasets, models)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2, Optional TLS/mTLS
    MLMD->>DB: INSERT artifact records<br/>MySQL/PostgreSQL protocol, Optional SSL
    DB-->>MLMD: Artifact IDs
    MLMD-->>KFP: PutArtifactsResponse

    KFP->>MLMD: PutEvents (artifact-execution links)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2, Optional TLS/mTLS
    MLMD->>DB: INSERT event records<br/>MySQL/PostgreSQL protocol, Optional SSL
    DB-->>MLMD: Success
    MLMD-->>KFP: PutEventsResponse

    Note over KFP,DB: Flow 2: Pipeline Artifact Lineage Query

    KFP->>MLMD: GetLineageGraph (artifact IDs)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2, Optional TLS/mTLS
    MLMD->>DB: SELECT lineage subgraph<br/>MySQL/PostgreSQL protocol, Optional SSL
    DB-->>MLMD: Artifacts, Executions, Events, Contexts
    MLMD-->>KFP: GetLineageGraphResponse<br/>Lineage subgraph with full provenance

    Note over KFP,DB: Flow 3: Context & Experiment Management

    KFP->>MLMD: PutContexts (experiment/pipeline)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2, Optional TLS/mTLS
    MLMD->>DB: INSERT context records<br/>MySQL/PostgreSQL protocol, Optional SSL
    DB-->>MLMD: Context IDs
    MLMD-->>KFP: PutContextsResponse

    KFP->>MLMD: PutAttributionsAndAssociations<br/>gRPC/HTTP2, Optional TLS/mTLS
    MLMD->>DB: INSERT attribution/association links<br/>MySQL/PostgreSQL protocol, Optional SSL
    DB-->>MLMD: Success
    MLMD-->>KFP: Response
